  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK918">
<l>āyu maṟiviṉa rallārk kaṇaṅkeṉpa</l>
<l> māya makaḷir muyakku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wise say that to such as are destitute of discerning sense the embraces of faithless women are (as ruinous as those of) the celestail female.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
